      "settings": {
        "heading": "Note from our Italian lab",
        "content": "<p>SerlinoLab is produced in a family-owned Italian lab, based in the Italian countryside, where every batch is made with hands-on care and strict quality control.</p><p>This isn’t mass production. It’s an authentic, controlled process designed for one thing: consistent results you can trust, batch after batch. That’s our core US selling point—Italian-made quality, done properly.</p><p><strong>— SerlinoLab</strong><br/>Family-made in Italy</p>",
